name: Schema Discriminator 1
title: Schema Discriminator 1: Urethra/Prostatic Urethra
notes:
**Note:** A schema discriminator is used to discriminate between urethra (male and female) and prostatic urethra. Code the site in which the tumor arose.

• **Urethra: Male Penile Urethra and Female Urethra (see code 1) **
Subsites include Urethra, NOS, Urethral Gland, Cowper gland

• **Urethra: Prostatic Urethra (see code 2) **
Subsites include Prostatic urethra, Prostatic utricle
